'''Tarasin Skintone Language''' was a complex form of communication thought to be one of the most beautiful languages in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]]. With this method, the [[Tarasin]] expressed their emotions and feelings&mdash;as well as thoughts and ideas&mdash;through a system of skin [[Color/Legends|color]] changes. [[Jorus Trass]], a [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] linguist, and other such [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]] deciphered and detailed the intricacies of the language in the document, ''[[Shades of Meaning]]''.

